reviewText: In the DVD she tells about her life before she joined the Supremes.  She also answers questions that fans often asked: "Why did she leave  the group?"  She provides clippings of her solo appearances after she left the Supremes. I was hoping to see at least one (who am I kidding I meant some) clipping of her performances with the Supremes. There are no clippings of these performances. She is a talented lady with a beautiful voice.
